data.description: Freshly renovated ranch style home is move-in ready! Offering a modern kitchen w/ luxurious granite counters, subway tile backsplash & white shaker cabinetry. Living area boasts ample space for entertaining, tons of natural light, & a gas fireplace. New plumbing & lighting fixtures, updated electrical & baths, & new HVAC upon accepted contract. Spacious patio w/ plenty of yard space. Two car attached garage. Set in an ideal location - close proximity to highways, shopping, dinning, and Lackland AFB.
